WEBVTT

00:09:59.031 --> 00:10:01.212
from your Fitbit, Spotify,

00:10:01.236 --> 00:10:02.810
social media accounts ...

00:10:03.405 --> 00:10:06.415
And you can choose
where to store your data,

00:10:06.439 --> 00:10:10.782
and digi.me will help you
to make your data work for you

00:10:10.806 --> 00:10:13.967
by providing insights that used
to be exclusively accessible

00:10:13.991 --> 00:10:15.645
by large data companies.

00:10:16.584 --> 00:10:21.481
In DC, a new initiative
called UBDI, U-B-D-I,

00:10:21.505 --> 00:10:23.922
Universal Basic Data Income,

00:10:23.946 --> 00:10:25.935
helps people to make money

00:10:25.959 --> 00:10:29.978
by sharing anonymous insights
through their data